:"Be part of something special in Berlin\'s most vibrant neighborhood","name":"Your Name","email":"Your Email","phone":"Phone (optional)","message":"Tell us about yourself, your experience, and why you want to join Zia Maria!","attachCv":"Attach CV","sendApplication":"Send Application"},"about":{"title":"About Us","subtitle":"Discover the story behind Zia Maria","sectionTitle":"More Than a Pizzeria","sectionSubtitle":"Where culinary art meets contemporary culture","heroLine1":"Where tradition meets innovation","heroLine2":"in the heart of Berlin\'s vibrant food scene","storyTitle":"A Slice of Berlin\'s Heart","storyP1":"Zia Maria is where passion for pizza meets art and a warm sense of community. Born as a family project, our restaurant blends the tradition of authentic Italian pizza with a friendly, creative atmosphere. We believe every pizza is a work of art, made with fresh ingredients and light, flavorful dough, and that food is a way to bring people together. We showcase local artists through rotating exhibitions, turning our space into a living gallery where guests can enjoy genuine flavors and be inspired. At Zia Maria, you come to eat well, feel at home, and discover something beautiful.","storyP2":"We blend traditional Italian techniques with Berlin\'s creative spirit, creating pizzas that are fresh, innovative, and unforgettable.","madeWithLove":"Made with love since 2007","stats":{"happyCustomers":"Happy Customers","avgRating":"Average Rating","uniquePizzas":"Unique Pizzas"}},"artSpace":{"description":"Our Art Space is a platform for local and international artists to showcase their work in an intimate, inspiring setting. We believe that great food and great art go hand in hand.","modalTitle":"Submit Your Project","modalIntro":"Share your idea with us. We support artists and projects aligned with our space.","fullNameLabel":"Full Name","placeholderFullName":"Your full name","emailLabel":"Email","placeholderEmail":"you@example.com","phoneLabel":"Phone (opt