s avec des ingr\xe9dients frais et de haute qualit\xe9. Consultez notre menu pour la s\xe9lection compl\xe8te.","q4":"Puis-je personnaliser ma pizza ?","a4":"Oui ! Vous pouvez ajouter ou retirer des ingr\xe9dients lors de la commande. Nous offrons \xe9galement des options sans gluten et pouvons accommoder la plupart des exigences alimentaires.","q5":"Quels sont vos horaires d\'ouverture ?","a5":"Nous sommes ouverts du lundi au samedi de 12:00 \xe0 22:00, et le dimanche de 12:00 \xe0 21:00.","q6":"Comment puis-je payer ma commande ?","a6":"Nous acceptons toutes les principales cartes de cr\xe9dit, PayPal et les paiements en esp\xe8ces. Les commandes en ligne peuvent \xeatre pay\xe9es en toute s\xe9curit\xe9 via notre syst\xe8me de paiement."}}'),tr:JSON.parse('{"common":{"home":"Ana Sayfa","menu":"Men\xfc","artSpace":"Sanat Alanı","about":"Hakkımızda","contact":"İletişim","joinUs":"Bize Katılın","reserve":"Rezervasyon","signIn":"Giriş Yap","logOut":"\xc7ıkış Yap","admin":"Y\xf6netici","user":"Kullanıcı","adminPanel":"Admin Paneli","language":"Dil","languageCode":"tr","navigation":"Navigasyon","loading":"Y\xfckleniyor...","optional":"İsteğe Bağlı","processing":"İşleniyor...","tryAgain":"Tekrar Dene","close":"Kapat","cancel":"İptal","backToMenu":"Men\xfcye D\xf6n","confirm":"Onayla","save":"Kaydet","edit":"D\xfczenle","delete":"Sil","add":"Ekle","remove":"Kaldır","select":"Se\xe7","search":"Ara","filter":"Filtrele","clear":"Temizle","next":"İleri","back":"Geri","continue":"Devam Et","finish":"Bitir","submit":"G\xf6nder","success":"Başarılı","failed":"Başarısız","submitProject":"Projenizi g\xf6nderin","active":"Aktif"},"checkout":{"title":"\xd6deme","orderSummary":"Sipariş \xd6zeti","subtotalVat":"Ara Toplam (KDV dahil)","total":"Toplam","steps":{"customerInformation":"M\xfcşteri Bilgileri","orderTiming":"Sipariş Zamanı","paymentMethod":"\xd6deme Y\xf6ntemi","reviewConfirm":"İncele ve Onayla"},"contactInformation":"İletişim Bilgileri","contactDescription":"L\xfctfen sip